# ABC049C - 白昼夢

## 問題

<https://atcoder.jp/contests/abs/tasks/arc065_a>

## 回答1

```elixir
defmodule Main do
  @words [
    "eraser",
    "erase",
    "dreamer",
    "dream"
  ]

  def main do
    :stdio
    |> IO.read(:all)
    |> solve()
    |> IO.puts()
  end

  def judge(""), do: "YES"

  def judge(_), do: "NO"

  def solve(input) do
    s = String.trim(input)

    Enum.reduce(@words, s, fn word, acc ->
      String.replace(acc, word, " ")
    end)
    |> String.trim()
    |> judge()
  end
end
```

```elixir
"""
erasedream
"""
|> Main.solve()
|> then(&(&1 == "YES"))
